{"word":"H1319 - בָּשַׂר - bâsar - baw-sar' - Messenger","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בָּשַׂר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>bâsar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>baw-sar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Messenger"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - செய்தியைக்கொண்டு போ, பிரசங்கி. நற்செய்தியைப் பிரசித்தப் படுத்து, சுவிசேஷத்தை அறிவி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to bear news, to bear tidings, to publish, to preach, to show forth"},{"paragraph":"a) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to gladden with good news"},{"paragraph":"2) to bear news"},{"paragraph":"3) to announce (salvation) as good news, to preach"},{"paragraph":"b) (Hithpael) to receive good news"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>be fresh</i>, that is, <i>full</i> (<i>rosy</i>, figuratively <i>cheerful</i>); to <i>announce</i> (glad news): - messenger, preach, publish, shew forth, (bear, bring, carry, preach, good, tell good) tidings."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1308 - בְּשֹׂור - Bᵉsôwr - bes-ore'/1308\">H1308</a>, <a href=\"#/H1309 - בְּשֹׂורָה - bᵉsôwrâh - bes-o-raw'/1309\">H1309</a>, <a href=\"#/H1319 - בָּשַׂר - bâsar - baw-sar'/1319\">H1319</a>, <a href=\"#/H1320 - בָּשָׂר - bâsâr - baw-sawr'/1320\">H1320</a>"}]}